The Portuguese Association of Tourist Guides and Tour Managers – AGIC – was legally founded in 2004 in order to represent and promote these professionals.
AGIC aims at providing high quality, competent, certified tourist guides and tour managers in different languages.
We offer services for individual travellers and/or groups for short and/or longer stays including:
• Roundtrips in Portugal;
• Local visits to cities;
- museums, churches and palaces;
• Walking tours;
• Cultural and theme tours;
• Schools;
• Taylor-made tours;
• Tour managers for international trips;
• Expert support in the organization of:
- meetings;
- incentives;
- congresses, and;
- events.

