FREE TOUR OF LISBON
Essential History & Fun Facts + Free Tastings
With The Most Entertaining and Passionate Local Guides you get to know:
* The historical neighborhoods of Bairro Alto, Chiado, Baixa (Downtown) and Alfama;
* The essential history of Portugal throughout the streets of Lisbon;
* Fun facts about the Portuguese people, their culture and their habits;
* Great sightseeing spots;
* A lot of smart tips to make the most of your vacation in Lisbon;
* And, free Tasting of the best Pastel de Nata (Portuguese Custard Tart) in Lisbon
​Free Tour is the common name for pay-what-you-wish tours (or pay-what-you-think-is-fair tours). You have the opportunity to take a tour with the best local guides in town an by the end you determine what the tour was worth (i.e.: 10€, 15€, 20€, …).

